The GIA premium for lab grown stones does not reflect a difference in the stone itself — it reflects a difference in the certification document. Both IGI and GIA grade lab grown diamonds on the same color and clarity scales, using the same grading instruments; for natural diamonds GIA is the gold standard, but for lab grown diamonds the GIA certification premium delivers no buyer benefit since resale value is near-zero regardless of certificate. Buy IGI for lab grown elongated cushions.

